original: Bengtsson, Carl Birger, stadsfiskal, Sölvesborg, f. 20/3/99 i Landskrona av handl. P. B. o. Johanna Persson. G. 46 m. Anna-Lisa Rossander. — Stud:ex. 17, jur. kand. 22. Tingstjg. 24-26, egen adv :verks. 27-29, stads-fiskal o. stadsfogde i Sölvesborg sed. 30.
translated: Bengtsson, Carl Birger, city prosecutor, Sölvesborg, b. March 20, 1899 in Landskrona to merchant P. B. and Johanna Persson. Married in 1946 to Anna-Lisa Rossander. — Graduated high school in 1917, graduated with a law degree in 1922. Worked in judicial district court from 1924-1926, had own law practice from 1927-1929, city prosecutor and municipal officer in Sölvesborg since 1930.
